{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SkateLab is a 100% physics-driven skateboarding sandbox built by a skateboarder, for people who love skateboarding.</h2>. . . . .<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/SLAB_Steam_CTRL7.gif?t=1729209061\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CONTROLS</h2>Starting with a fresh take on dual-stick board control, SkateLab was designed to prioritize responsiveness above anything.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WHAT'S THE MOTIVATION?</h2>For now.. just skate! We're launching into early access as a <i>sandbox</i> where you're likely to get lost in the mechanics of skateboarding. Master the controls and develop a style naturally through your own movement.<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/MPStatic_600W.png?t=1729209061\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MULTIPLAYER FREE-SKATE</h2>Enjoy skating the way you want to, with who you want to - whether that's alone or with friends!<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/SLAB_Steam_Dropper.gif?t=1729209061\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BUILD SPOTS</h2>Use the object-dropper to build and modify your very own skate spots! Move, Rotate, Scale, and even Bend objects for endless possibilities.<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/SLAB_Steam_REPLAY.gif?t=1729209061\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REPLAYS</h2>Look back at your best tricks! Rewind, play, and record with your favorite screen capturing software!<br><br>. . . .","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2983940?t=1729209061","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1729209061","capsule_image":"https://share